{"tid":1718903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手足們，有時整RB可唔可以諗下有手足接放學。","createTime":"2019-11-14T03:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T03:46:24.000Z","uid":216105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c88918c4d3b2531e3ab710cff3858e7d93cec4b2","tid":1718903,"uid":216105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:17:15.000Z","msg":"前日有人接放學，送物資去中大嘅時候，喺第一城畫紡十字路囗，一城大涌橋十字路口。<br />\n手足們果個位有需要rb？好多人經果道去火炭幫手，但因為地上面有玻璃同磚，搞到部車中招。<br />\n<br />\n手足們如果你地係想三罷，可唔可以差唔多返工時間先搞，十一二點真係搞尻到其他接放學手足。<br />\n<br />\n個人意見，有錯勿插"},{"pid":"24d53a534f5dadd56afcfc9946af51d11bb43c60","tid":1718903,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:34:30.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"6532e74d921b84f62a6713cf19d1ee99382b6fac","tid":1718903,"uid":322023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:45:31.000Z","msg":"Sorry 吖，唔係好熟手，想問下啲RB整喺邊，咩時候整先有最大功用又唔會阻到手足？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a2654963c4b58f99cd056ea7aea25a8ad9c0e7","tid":1718903,"uid":322023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6532e74d921b84f62a6713cf19d1ee99382b6fac","tid":1718903,"uid":322023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:45:31.000Z","msg":"Sorry 吖，唔係好熟手，想問下啲RB整喺邊，咩時候整先有最大功用又唔會阻到手足？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:46:24.000Z","msg":"我指發夢嗰陣"}]}